Description:
JEWEL IN CRIB POINT
Totally renovated 3/4 bedrooms family home set on a generous 1011m2 allotment offers modern comfort, privacy and character.
Lovely natural light and solid timber floor boards flow throughout the home. The front lounge room features gas fire and over looks private front gardens. 3 Tanks providing 7000 litres service surrounding gardens.
A thoughtfully designed central kitchen includes an island bench, dishwasher, pantry, 5 burner stainless steel midea gas oven and adjoins a large rumpus room and undercover alfresco area.
The alfresco deck built with entertaining and family gatherings in mind features coonara fire, BBQ area and cafe blinds, perfect for entertaining family and friends.
Other features include 2 split system air - conditioners, gas space heater, built in robes and plenty of storage. The master bedroom offers walk in robe, ensuite and its own private deck and garden.
Outside features a powered work shop with loft, storage, garage and cubby or art studio. A massive carport with extra height clearence will accommodate boat, caravan and at least 4 vehicles.
Close to local schools, a short walk to public transport and local shops, a inspection of this property is a must see.

Address: 256 Stony Point Road Crib Point VIC 3919
Description:
Classic family cottage
Fixed Date Sale - Closing 28th May, 2019
Located right in the heart of Crib Point just a leisurely stroll to schools, shops and transport this classic period-style family home on a generous 719m2 (approx.) block will be at the top of your list if you're after a lifestyle or a fantastic investment.
You'll love the versatile layout offering plenty of room to grow with 4 bedrooms (master with robes), 2 spacious living areas under soaring 11 ft ceilings, a defined rumpus for the kids and a family bathroom with separate WC. A large central kitchen has been stylishly updated with stone benchtops and provides ample storage space & work surfaces.
There's plenty to admire outside as well with an undercover alfresco deck perfect for year-round entertaining, a brilliant fully-fenced backyard for the kids to play, and a fenced above-ground swimming pool in a newly tiled setting.
Extra's include 2 gas fireplaces, split-system air-conditioning and ceiling fans, rear laundry, garden shed and double carport with sensor lights, with off-road parking space for an additional 3 vehicles.
In a tranquil, family-friendly location just minutes to amenities, HMAS Cerberus Naval Base and the Stony Point boat ramp & ferry service this charming property has much to offer and is sure to appeal to young families, investors or developers. Call Joel Hood or Adrian Calcedo today to arrange your inspection.

Description:
A Unique Opportunity Awaits... The Old Crib Point Fire Station
** Please note this is a working fire station at the moment. Inspections may be cancelled at short notice **
Located in the heart of a wonderful community, the Crib Point CFA Fire station is on offer for sale by auction. Don't miss this unique opportunity to secure what could potentially be a multitude of options.
Situated on a generous parcel of 770sqm (approx.) of Residentially Zoned land, this property has been the home to the crib point fire station for the last 50 years (approximately) and is now ready to be put to use as your heart desires.
Consisting of shedding for up to 5 vehicles (approx.), with one main building and an adjacent smaller shed, a kitchen and meeting room facility and bathroom facilities, along with an outdoor pergola area overlooking a pleasant and peaceful rear yard.
The property will be sold with vacant possession due to the Crib Point branch relocating to a new site, so this offers the potential to develop the existing shedding or develop the land (STCA) and other beneficial uses.
This could be your dream come true or the opportunity you have been waiting for, with such a fantastic location, a generous allotment and residential zoning this property offers prime potential!

Description:
An Immaculate All-Rounder
Sitting pretty, amongst mature gardens and a backdrop of trees, on a rare and generous allotment of 1000sqm (approx.), this well-maintained family home will meet many a perspective purchasers' requirements! With an abundance of charm and features to match, this property is one not to be missed, opportunities like this don't arise often!
Upon entering the home, you will be greeted by a formal lounge and open study space, featuring soft neutral tones, stunning arched entries and ornate cornices & elegant light fittings throughout. With three living zones on offer (Formal lounge, open plan living off kitchen and rear rumpus room/recreational area) this home provides more than most when it comes to space for families, growing or established!
Internally, the home features a generous master with walk in robe and ensuite with separate toilet and large shower, a further two sizeable bedrooms with BIR's which are serviced by the main family bathroom with spa bath, separate W/C and a generous laundry with double linen, additional cupboard & external access to the rear yard. A spacious kitchen centres itself in the home with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, gas cook top and built in oven (& a fridge should you like it), marbled vinyl benches tie in perfectly with the neutral hues of the home and overlooks the family/meals area and courtyard alfresco. Further modern conveniences consist of gas ducted heating, split system cooling (2 Units), ceiling fans, brand new carpets throughout & double lock up garage with rear roller door and direct access.
Externally, besides the gorgeous grounds, fruit trees, manicured gardens & pergola, the property offers a HUGE, 3 roller door, 9 X 14 Metre Shed, with work benches, power, and the ideal addition for tradespeople, motor enthusiasts or that boat/caravan...or both? Offering gated side access to the shedding at the rear which could easily accommodate 6 vehicles, there is also ample room for secure off-street parking plus the double lock up remote garage. With a quarter acre of peninsula paradise this property also has additional garden shedding, 3 large water tanks & a vegetable garden area.
Properties like this don't pop up often, so don't miss out on what could be your dream home! With multiple living zones, side access and ample car accommodation on a spacious allotment, this home is sure to please!
Contact Jason Dowler anytime to arrange your inspection!
